data.description: Upgrades throughout home! This 3 bedroom home also has a 4th bedroom that is framed with electrical! Just needs those final touches.  2 baths on main floor, plumbed for 3rd bath in basement, plus a 2 car garage.  Kitchen has newer cabinetry, flooring plus a spacious pantry! Home has new paint plus new flooring which includes carpet & Premium Vinyl Flooring! Spacious living room with bay window.  Good size master bedroom with full size bath & jetted tub!  Nice landscaping in the front yard and backyard, which includes a deck & fully landscaped with above ground swimming pool for summer fun!  Basement is partially finished with family room plus another room that could be used as an office, play room, exercise room or craft area!  The framed  basement for the 4th bedroom just needs sheetrock, flooring & some final personal touches! (Permit has been pulled) Smart thermostat & Door Bell. New water heater.
